---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Experience | My Portfolio" lang="en">
  <section>
    <h2>Experience</h2>

    <article>
      <h3>Backend Development Intern — Infone</h3>
      <p class="date">
        <time datetime="2025-09">September 2025</time> — <time
          datetime="2025-11">November 2025</time
        >
      </p>

      <p>
        During my curricular internship at the startup <strong>Infone</strong>,
        I actively participated in their expansion into the real estate sector.
        My role focused on designing and developing critical automation
        processes for their business model from scratch:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Real Estate Classification Pipeline:</strong> Designed and implemented
          an automated pipeline in FastAPI to determine the financial viability of
          clients. The system automates the matching between user profiles and eligible
          housing.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Data Extraction (OCR):</strong> Integrated <strong
            >AWS Textract</strong
          > and <strong>S3</strong> to process documents (PDFs and images), achieving
          automated data extraction and eliminating manual workflows.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Traceability and Observability:</strong> Implemented a structured
          logging system using <strong>structlog</strong>, significantly
          improving system monitoring and production error resolution.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Web Scraping:</strong> Researched and developed solutions with <strong
            >Browserbase (Stagehand)</strong
          > for the automated location of real estate assets listed by private owners.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Soft Skills:</strong> The remote startup environment enhanced my
          capacity for <strong>autonomous work</strong>, time management, and
          technical proactivity.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/SergioMulet/OCR-payslip-evaluator"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">View repository</a
        >
      </p>
      <p class="stack-list">
        <strong>Stack:</strong> Python, FastAPI, AWS (S3, Textract), Structlog, Browserbase,
        Git.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
